OL,3,CWorkers 'cheated' out of holiday pay `
OL,4,CTUC
OL,6,FThe main reasons included a culture
OL,7,Fwhere workers feared asking for paid
OL,8,Ftime off could lead to them being
OL,9,Ftreated unfavourably, staff struggling
OL,10,Fwith unrealistic workloads that did
OL,11,Fnot allow time to take leave, as well
OL,12,Fas requests being turned down, said
OL,13,Fthe TUC.
OL,15,FThe report, published to mark the
OL,16,Fbeginning of the TUC's annual Congress
OL,17,Fon Sunday, said the "missing weeks" of
OL,18,Fholiday paid added up to #1,800 per
OL,19,Faffected employee.
