OL,3,CWorkers 'cheated' out of holiday pay `
OL,4,CTUC
OL,6,FThe research indicated that black and
OL,7,Fminority ethnic (BME) staff were
OL,8,Fhardest hit, with 6% not getting any
OL,9,Fpaid holiday last year, compared to 4%
OL,10,Fof white employees.
OL,12,FThe jobs with the highest numbers of
OL,13,Fstaff losing out were waiters and
OL,14,Fwaitresses (59,000), care workers and
OL,15,Fhome carers (55,000), and kitchen and
OL,16,Fcatering assistants (50,000), showing
OL,17,Fthat low paid workers were most at
OL,18,Frisk of losing paid holiday
OL,19,Fentitlement, said the report.
