OL,3,CWorkers 'cheated' out of holiday pay `
OL,4,CTUC
OL,6,FThe TUC is supporting Labour's plans
OL,7,Ffor a Fair Work Agency and has accused
OL,8,Fthe previous Conservative government
OL,9,Fof allowing bad employers to cheat
OL,10,Fstaff out of basic workplace rights.
OL,12,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,13,F"We all deserve a break from work to
OL,14,Fspend time off with our friends and
OL,15,Ffamily, but more than a million
OL,16,Fworking people have been deprived of
OL,17,Fany of the paid leave they are due,
OL,18,Fand hundreds of thousands more have
OL,19,Fbeen denied basic rights like being
OL,20,Fpaid the minimum wage.
