OL,4,CTUC
OL,6,F"The Conservative government sat back
OL,7,Fand let bad employers cheat their
OL,8,Fstaff out of their basic workplace
OL,9,Frights.
OL,11,F"Tory ministers were more concerned
OL,12,Fabout stopping people getting what
OL,13,Fthey were due by introducing anti-
OL,14,Funion measures, than funding
OL,15,Fenforcement bodies properly.
OL,17,F"Now it's time to reset the dial and
OL,18,Fto end the Tories' race to the bottom.
